# VUTTR
Very Useful Tools to Remember.

# Group Tools
This section groups tool resources.

## Tool [/tools/{tool_id}]
A Tool is the central object utilized.

+ Parameters
    + tool_id: `1` (string) - The id of the Tool.

+ Model (application/json)

    ```js
    {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Notion",
        "link": "https://notion.so",
        "description": "All in one tool to organize teams and ideas. Write, plan, collaborate, and get organized. ",
        "tags": [
            "organization",
            "planning",
            "collaboration",
            "writing",
            "calendar"
        ]
    }
    ```

### Retrieve a Tool [GET]
Returns a specific Tool.

+ Response 200

    [Tool][]

### Delete a Tool [DELETE]
Delete a Tool.

+ Response 204

