### Create a Tool [POST]
Create a new Tool object.

+ Request

    [Tool][]

+ Response 201

    [Tool][]

### Retrieve all Tools [GET]
Retrieves all tools.

+ Parameters

    + tag (string, optional) - Search for tools within this tag.

+ Response 200

    [Tools Collection][]